[SN]TITLE[SN]
Manhunt after armed Reading bookmaker's raid

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police are hunting a man, thought to be carrying a gun, who threatened staff and a customer in a raid on a bookmaker's in Reading.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The offender stole a quantity of cash from Ladbrokes in Basingstoke Road on Saturday night.
No-one was injured but police have appealed for information.
The man was white, in his mid-20s to mid-30s, and about 6ft (1.82m) tall. He wore a black and white hooded top with a yellow cap.
